2026-05-16T20:22:36.6655418Z 21    <!--
2026-05-16T20:22:36.6655888Z 22        Exact alarm permissions. We request both so reminders fire reliably
2026-05-16T20:22:36.6656077Z 23        across Android versions:
2026-05-16T20:22:36.6656417Z 24          - SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM: required on Android 12 (API 31-32); the
2026-05-16T20:22:36.6656962Z 25            user must toggle it on via Settings. We prompt for this in
2026-05-16T20:22:36.6657295Z 26            MainActivity when canScheduleExactAlarms() returns false.
2026-05-16T20:22:36.6657624Z 27          - USE_EXACT_ALARM: auto-granted on Android 13+ (API 33+) for
2026-05-16T20:22:36.6658076Z 28            calendar/reminder/timer-style apps, so no prompt is needed.
2026-05-16T20:22:36.6658404Z 29        Without USE_EXACT_ALARM the app was silently falling back to
2026-05-16T20:22:36.6658739Z 30        inexact alarms on Android 13+, which Samsung (and other OEMs)
2026-05-16T20:22:36.6659029Z 31        aggressively delay or drop under Doze/App Standby.
2026-05-16T20:22:36.6659195Z 32    -->
2026-05-16T20:22:36.6659608Z 33    <uses-permission android:name="android.permission.SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM" />
