2026-05-16T20:22:36.6898009Z 271            Harden Google Play Billing's proxy activities so the system
2026-05-16T20:22:36.6898349Z 272            cannot restore them from Recents or after process death with a
2026-05-16T20:22:36.6898705Z 273            stale Intent. The library's onCreate reads the PendingIntent
2026-05-16T20:22:36.6899066Z 274            extra without null-checking; if Android recreates the activity
2026-05-16T20:22:36.6899308Z 275            and the extra is missing, it NPEs on
2026-05-16T20:22:36.6899661Z 276            PendingIntent.getIntentSender(). noHistory + excludeFromRecents
2026-05-16T20:22:36.6900007Z 277            finishes the activity as soon as it leaves the foreground so it
2026-05-16T20:22:36.6900334Z 278            is never re-entered with a missing extra. Library 8.x adds its
2026-05-16T20:22:36.6900681Z 279            own configChanges absorber and a v2 proxy, both of which we
